18
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:07,650
Pas vraiment.

19
00:02:09,450 --> 00:02:13,550
Mais j'ai toujours su... ce que je ne voulais pas !

20
00:02:14,125 --> 00:02:14,650
Ha...

21
00:02:15,125 --> 00:02:16,375
Meurs,

22
00:02:16,450 --> 00:02:17,750
Dottore.

23
00:02:25,075 --> 00:02:25,850
Non !

24
00:02:33,375 --> 00:02:34,490
Et maintenant...

25
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:37,000
Vous avez échoué.

